1     PIN_FLD_NAME            STR [0] "/audit_account_products"
1     PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "The audit_account_products object is OBSOLETE and objects of this type are no longer created in Infranet release 6.7 and above.During upgradation from lower versions of Infranet to Infranet 6.7 and above ,the audit_account_products will have existing old data pertaining to lower release ,this data will be used for re-rating of old events . This  object is  used to  save obsoleted  account product for one account.It has most fields in the account products array in /account object except the PIN_FLD_LAST_MODIFIED_T and it has extra fields to mark the effective time of this product within the account. When re-rating an event or rating a backdated event, products which are effective at the event time will be used as the account products. "
