2         PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "Used to track the billing status of a billinfo. Legal values are PIN_BILL_ACTIVE - indicates that billing should be provided for the account in a standard (regular) way. This is a default value. PIN_BILL_INACTIVE - indicates that billing should be suspended for the billinfo. PIN_BILL_ERROR - indicates that an error occurred when the billing application tried to bill this billinfo. If an error occurs for a subordinate billinfo, the parent billinfo's status will also be set to PIN_BILL_ERROR."
