1     PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "A singleton configuration object this class contains information on all Infranet resources. Resources can be either currency or non-currency resources. User-defined resources must have numeric resource id value greater than 1,000,000. Numeric ids for the currency resources are defined as per the ISO 4217 standard.  A sample file pin_beid that can be used with load_pin_beid is shipped with Portal system. These resources must not be changed after loading them into the database."
