1     PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "A single configuration object of this class defines the General Ledger (GL) Chart of Accounts (COA) used in the  customer's financial system. This object contains information  such as the accounts used in the COA, the type and the  status of these accounts. This information is used to  validate the accounts defined each GLID in a given  gl_segment. The /config/gl_chartaccts object is loaded  using the load_pin_gl_chartaccts utility. "
