1     PIN_FLD_NAME            STR [0] "/group/sponsor"
1     PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "Sponsored billing allows one customer to pay for part of one or more other customers' bills. Sponsored billing also allows one customer to pay another customer directly.  Sponsored billing is managed by setting up sponsored groups. A sponsored group consists of one sponsoring account, and one or more accounts that the sponsor pays for. An account can sponsor more than one group, and an account can be sponsored by more than one account group.  The sponsorer is referred to by the PIN_FLD_PARENT field in the base /group object."
1     PIN_FLD_LABEL           STR [0] "Sponsorship group object"
