1     PIN_FLD_NAME            STR [0] "/item"
1     PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "Item objects represent A/R in Infranet. Any impact to an account's A/R is stored and tracked in an /item object. This includes not only fees and usage charges, but also payments, adjustments, disputes and refunds. Events always belong to one or more /item objects. The impact from any event can be traced to the /item tracking that A/R. Some /item objects belong to a /bill object (cycle fees, usage, etc), while others are direct A/R and do not belong to any bill (payments, refunds, etc). See /event."
