3             PIN_FLD_FIELD_NAME      STR [0] "PIN_FLD_GL_REPORT_POID_LIST"
3             PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "Contains a list of 1, 2 or 3 /ledger_report POIDs. The first one represents the basic report generated using ledger report opcode. If there are 2 POIDs, the second one is either the custom report generated after execution of PCM_OP_GL_POL_EXPORT_GL policy opcode (in the case of report types Billed, Billed earned and Previously billed earned) or the incremental report created using ledger report for previous period (in the case of report types Unbilled, Unbilled earned, Unbilled unearned and Billed unearned). If there are 3 POIDs, the second one is the custom report and the third one is the incremental report."
